title: Tikhatar
text:
Tikhatar is a <a href="Village%20development%20committee%20%28Nepal%29">village development committee</a> in <a href="Doti%20District">Doti District</a> in the <a href="Seti%20Zone">Seti Zone</a> of western <a href="Nepal">Nepal</a>. At the time of the <a href="1991%20Nepal%20census">1991 Nepal census</a> it had a population of 5222 people in 958 individual households.
